    <summary>Gaming Input Peripherals Device Firewall for Windows</summary>
    <description>
HidHide is an "input device firewall" inspired by HidGuardian but designed and written from scratch.
It allows for blocking individual applications access to HID and XInput devices, allowing users to re-route and re-map controller inputs as they please.
